channel.title: Error version TWO
channel.description:
After figuring out how to navigate the forums and downloading B2300's 1.6.6 bin, I went to execute the jar file. Further more, I was proceeded by the following error:
Failed to load Main-Class manifest attribute from C:\Users\Anthony\Desktop\minecraft-1.6.6.jar
Thoughts, concerns, answers Dr. Phil?
